Queen - Class in com.chess.piece
Queen class is a child class of the Piece class It deals with the construction and movement of the Queen piece on the board and other specific methods needed for the Queen piece The methods found here are: calculateLegalMove(), movePiece(), isColA(), isColH(), and toString()
